v/t2/f2/m367/AQP6S5z6Ky-4Eswfl1trTDwqTNInMl1Ttzhl3LUlX4N-6v3tabWD0Xx9sMGO1FXbGUUzcO5a_z5cVNepD6tEbIbJ3PoXJDsSsgcxGQ0.mp4?_nc_cat=110&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=uII5x8ZSszIQ7kNvwGMpPWW&%3D&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=BXwbh8eqou8C7lyZh--MlA&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ss=7a32e&oh=00_Af1bRQTZl7vogr2OH4vvik4EnPfTAvLzC5iYsHJL1Tw-ZQ&oe=69D79143", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 396466, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/91.0.4472.164 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 51.238, "format": "dash-820988014344278v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by sheturnedsavage", "description": "No one talks about this part.\n\nWhen pain has been your shadow for years,\nit stops feeling like something you carry —\nand starts feeling like who you are.\n\nYou’ve built yourself around it.\nLearned how to function with it.\nLearned how to explain yourself through it.\n\nThe sadness became your language.\nThe anxiety became your rhythm.\nThe grief became your identity.\n\nSo when someone says, “You’re healing,”\ninstead of relief… there’s fear.\n\nWho am I without the ache?\nWho am I without the story that shaped me?\nWho am I without the battles that carved themselves into my bones?\n\nHealing sounds beautiful in theory.\nBut in reality?\nIt feels like walking into a quiet room after years of chaos.\n\nAnd the quiet is unfamiliar.\nThe quiet is uncomfortable.\nThe quiet asks you to meet yourself without the armor.\n\nYou are not strange for being scared of that.\nYou are not weak for hesitating at the edge of peace.\n\nWhen pain has been your compass,\nletting it go can feel like losing direction.\n\nBut here’s the truth:\n\nYou are not your suffering.\nYou are not the worst thing that happened to you.\nYou are not the grief that shaped you.\n\nYou are the person who survived it.\n\nAnd the version of you that exists beyond the pain?\nShe isn’t empty.\nShe isn’t lost.\nShe isn’t unrecognisable.\n\nShe’s softer.\nStronger.\nQuieter in the best way.\n\nIt’s okay to be scared of meeting her.\n\nJust don’t run from her.\n\n🕊️ Follow @sheturnedsavage for grief quotes that hold your heart while you learn who you are outside the hurt.\n\n💬 If you’re struggling with your mental health and navigating healing feels overwhelming,\ncomment or DM “workbook.”\nYou don’t have to figure this out alone.\n\n#HealingIsScary\n#GriefJourney\n#IdentityAfterLoss\n#MentalHealthHealing\n#BecomingAfterBreakdown\n\nfear of healing, identity after trauma, grief and self discovery, healing anxiety support, emotional growth after loss, who am I without my pain, trauma identity shift, mental health recovery journey, learning to live without grief, healing feels unfamiliar, coping with long term sadness, emotional transformation process, overcoming fear of change, grief and personal growth, becoming after trauma\n\nDisclaimer; no copyright intended 🤍", "duration": 61.902, "timestamp": 1771371900, "uploader_id": "74856251976", "uploader": "Sar | Grief & Healing Quotes 🕊️", "channel": "sheturnedsavage", "like_count": 56414, "comment_count": 331, "comments": [{"author": "bubbles16lexi", "author_id": "57096039722", "id": "18090455813272787", "text": "relatable", "timestamp": 1775350926}, {"author": "bonnet_babe_variety", "author_id": "58868219047", "id": "18312951430283996", "text": "Finally someone understands 😢", "timestamp": 1775320440}, {"author": "irenahrm", "author_id": "59952657780", "id": "18149233036468839", "text": "♡", "timestamp": 1775307230}, {"author": "lifeof_mymyyy3xx_", "author_id": "57865201818", "id": "18079198742116993", "text": "Real", "timestamp": 1775305071}, {"author": "theonlygirlwith_76", "author_id": "12134950550", "id": "18577265632048292", "text": "No one will understand me", "timestamp": 1775295483}, {"author": "ali_.lea", "author_id": "5801083320", "id": "17955262716110930", "text": "I once wrote something when I was losing my mind and going through a lot years ago. I forever have it etched into my soul when I reread. \n\n“I can’t heal. I need to tear open my old wounds. I need to bleed. I need to scream from the pain. To know it was true. To PROVE it was REAL.”", "timestamp": 1775265091}, {"author": "laidback7126", "author_id": "36730144621", "id": "18177580156377573", "text": "Good night sweet dreams", "timestamp": 1775262057}, {"author": "coffee_peaches", "author_id": "48151361992", "id": "17852849406646476", "text": "Never heard something so true!! I'm trying so hard to heal but I'm it's so challenging! Sending love to everyone who is feeling the same ❤️❤️", "timestamp": 1775257836}, {"author": "karawarner77", "author_id": "70193737643", "id": "18094889615119943", "text": "", "timestamp": 1775257343}, {"author": "puprauer", "author_id": "1043005740", "id": "18059013872452328", "text": "This is absolutely me😢😢😢", "timestamp": 1775249874}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/639935249_17877931773491977_3651349390872546567_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p640x640_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi43MjB4MTI4MC5zZHIuZjgyNzg3LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=101&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGX6jpBj9hEC7ls-iQ4a1LS15etkU7synmFmZi6AOTMFan8PgJEsRUzXU_0niJIhP4&_nc_ohc=uLk6u8JPxrEQ7kNvwFhHymV&_nc_gid=BXwbh8eqou8C7lyZh--MlA&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af12xA1XePXmtY8FhbE0-8bKe9dMYHuqdvWtcXqfpksKuQ&oe=69D7A1A7&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1137, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1137"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/639935249_17877931773491977_3651349390872546567_n.jpg?stp